exports[`Banner Seed 1`] = `
"<pre class="m-0 max-w-[700px] whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-md border border-border bg-card/40 p-3 font-mono text-[11px] text-teal-200 leading-[1.5]">Add everything that isn't in my nix config yet:
- 11 apps installed by hand (would land in modules/darwin/homebrew.nix)
   - docker (Docker Desktop · 4.32.0)
   - obs (OBS Studio · 30.2.3)
   - iterm2 (iTerm2 · 3.5.1)
   - vlc (VLC media player · 3.0.20)
   - figma (Figma · 124.4.0)
   - spotify (Spotify · 1.2.45)
   - slack (Slack · 4.40.0)
   - zoom (Zoom · 6.1.10)
   - discord (Discord · 0.0.310)
   - notion (Notion · 4.1.0)
   - audacity (Audacity · 3.6.4)
- 8 settings differ from defaults (would land in modules/darwin/defaults.nix)
   - Dock — magnification on (com.apple.dock magnification = 1)
   - Finder — show path bar (com.apple.finder ShowPathbar = 1)
   - Trackpad — three-finger drag (com.apple.AppleMultitouchTrackpad TrackpadThreeFingerDrag = 1)
   - Keyboard — fast key repeat (NSGlobalDomain KeyRepeat = 2)
   - Mission Control — disable rearrange (com.apple.dock mru-spaces = 0)
   - Hot corners — bottom-right: lock screen (com.apple.dock wvous-br-corner = 13)
   - Menu bar — show date (com.apple.menuextra.clock DateFormat = "EEE MMM d  h:mm a")
   - Sound — feedback off (NSGlobalDomain com.apple.sound.uiaudio.enabled = 0)
- 4 apps auto-start at login (would land in modules/darwin/services.nix)
   - Rectangle (/Applications/Rectangle.app)
   - Raycast (/Applications/Raycast.app)
   - 1Password (/Applications/1Password.app)
   - Hammerspoon (/Applications/Hammerspoon.app)
</pre>"
`;

